Function Remove-ObjectsFromPortal {
<#
	.SYNOPSIS
	Removes all objects of a certain type from the FIM Portal.

	.DESCRIPTION
	Removes all objects of a certain type from the FIM Portal.

	.EXAMPLE
	Remove-ObjectsFromPortal -ObjectType "Person"
#>
